      • createNewUser

        public java.lang.String createNewUser()
        This method checks whether the Servlet got the token information from a logic part. In case the token was read and the new user name was provided, it writes information about new user to the configuration file.
        Returns:
        page with list of users in case of successful creation of a new user. Otherwise redirects to the current page.
